content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/charizardite-x\/03-pokemon-unbound-pushing-the-boulder-north.jpg\" alt=\"Pushing the boulder north. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Pushing the boulder north.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you can\u2019t push the boulder north anymore, start pushing it east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/charizardite-x\/04-pokemon-unbound-pushing-the-boulder-east-when-the-path-north-runs-out.jpg\" alt=\"Pushing the boulder east when the path north runs out. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Pushing the boulder east when the path north runs out.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Push the boulder on top of the white pressure plate. Then follow the newly-created path of rocks you can jump over to get to the other side.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/charizardite-x\/05-pokemon-unbound-pushing-the-boulder-on-top-of-the-pressure-plate.jpg\" alt=\"Pushing the boulder on top of the pressure plate. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Pushing the boulder on top of the pressure plate.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After getting to the other side, climb the northern stairs to see a cave you can enter. Head inside.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/charizardite-x\/06-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-newly-opened-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the newly-opened cave. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the newly-opened cave.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Charizardite X is inside this room, on the ground behind the Raid Den.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/charizardite-x\/07-pokemon-unbound-finding-the-charizardite-x.jpg\" alt=\"Finding the Charizardite X. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Finding the Charizardite X.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Mega Stones<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1711,"parent":278,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[12],"class_list":["post-1710","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-mega-stones"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1710","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/278"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1711"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1710"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1710"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}